56
00:05:14,387 --> 00:05:15,402
Let's go!

57
00:05:15,475 --> 00:05:16,460
Don't forget the parsley!

58
00:05:16,756 --> 00:05:18,165
Make sure it's clean!

59
00:05:28,768 --> 00:05:30,844
<i>Everyone knew</i>
<i>Chef Andre was a genius,</i>

60
