year's royal creation.</i>

63
00:05:55,004 --> 00:05:56,085
More onions!

64
00:05:56,158 --> 00:05:57,142
More onions!

65
00:05:57,247 --> 00:05:58,231
More onions!

66
00:05:58,337 --> 00:05:59,351
More onions!

67
00:06:00,931 --> 00:06:02,820
<i>They would jam the town square,</i>

68
00:06:02,886 --> 00:06:05,091
<i>and, as the aroma began to build,</i>

69
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,202
<i>so did their anticipation.</i>

70
00:06:09,740 --> 00:06:11,564
- Ohhh!
- Ow!

71
