Sorry.

72
00:06:20,758 --> 00:06:21,774
Wow.

73
00:06:24,445 --> 00:06:25,459
Thank you.

74
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:31,392
It's my pleasure to announce
this year's royal creations

75
