Oh. Evening.

112
00:08:17,810 --> 00:08:22,071
I don't have to stand here
and listen to a big talking garbage can!

113
00:08:22,232 --> 00:08:25,716
Ha! And I don't have
to stand here and listen to a coward!

114
00:08:26,012 --> 00:08:27,507
- Coward?
- Yes, a coward!

115
00:08:27,612 --> 00:08:29,372
- You call me coward?
- Yes!

116
00:08:33,283 --> 00:08:34,691
Oh, no!

117
00:08:51,511 --> 00:08:52,940
Oh, no, no, no, no, no.

118
00:08:53,047 --> 00:08:54,544
That did it.

119
00:08:58,749 --> 00:09:00,443
- Hmm?
- Mmm.

120
00:09:00,832 --> 00:09:02,111
Mmm!

121
00:09:04,035 --> 00:09:06,177
<i>- Bellissima!</i>
- It's <i>fantastique!</i>

122
00:09:06,247 --> 00:09:09,096
Roscuro! Roscuro, where are you?

123
00:09:12,204 --> 00:09:13,284
Ohhh.

124
00:09:32,865 --> 00:09:34,044
Whoa!

125
00:09:54,872 --> 00:09:55,985
<i>Voil?</i>

126
00:09:56,250 --> 00:09:59,188
This is amazing!

127
00:09:59,421 --> 00:10:01,047
Wait till
Your Highness tastes it.

128
00:10:03,235 --> 00:10:04,218
Hmm?

129
00:10:15,599 --> 00:10:16,907
This is...

130
00:10:17,006 --> 00:10:17,991
Whoa!

131
00:10:18,097 --> 00:10:20,008
...absolutely...

132
