1055
01:13:51,345 --> 01:13:52,841
Let's go!

1056
01:13:53,332 --> 01:13:55,186
Into the breach!

1057
01:13:56,501 --> 01:13:57,485
Down there.

1058
01:13:57,592 --> 01:13:58,903
