1068
01:14:38,466 --> 01:14:39,614
Come on, let's go!

1069
01:14:40,997 --> 01:14:44,132
Oi! Hang on! Where you going? Help!

1070
01:14:47,019 --> 01:14:48,034
Hurry!

1071
01:14:49,647 --> 01:14:50,630
Look at that!

1072
01:14:50,960 --> 01:14:52,388
Let's get him, boys.

1073
01:15:01,725 --> 01:15:03,479
Ow! Ow, ow, ow!

1074
01:15:05,247 --> 01:15:06,231
Keep going! Keep going!

1075
01:15:06,337 --> 01:15:08,159
Please! Oh, no, get off of me!

