Nice shot!

1077
01:15:16,425 --> 01:15:17,410
That's my onion!

1078
01:15:38,178 --> 01:15:39,605
Hello?

1079
01:15:39,714 --> 01:15:40,730
Help!

1080
01:15:41,733 --> 01:15:43,644
Help!

1081
01:15:43,720 --> 01:15:45,061
Can anybody hear me?

1082
01:15:47,051 --> 01:15:48,513
Help!

1083
01:15:49,547 --> 01:15:51,373
I'm in here!

1084
01:15:53,457 --> 01:15:54,767
I'm in here!

1085
01:15:55,571 --> 01:15:56,980
I'm in here!

1086
01:16:05,180 --> 01:16:06,197
Oh, gor!

1087
01:16:06,943 --> 01:16:08,505
What took you so long?

1088
01:16:08,609 --> 01:16:12,027
