for over two hours.

1089
01:16:13,768 --> 01:16:16,069
My little princess.

1090
01:16:19,886 --> 01:16:20,932
Rain.

1091
01:16:21,005 --> 01:16:21,989
Yes.

1092
01:16:30,106 --> 01:16:31,731
